data.description: Explore this captivating 4-bed, 2-bath pool home nestled in the coveted Scottsdale East Estates. Offering a delightful blend of spaces including living and family rooms, a dining area, and an open-plan kitchen, this charming abode boasts a saltwater heated pool and solar. Plus, there's a convenient shed outside. Don't miss the chance to experience this desirable residence!
